WEBVTT

00:05.798 --> 00:08.032
Such a shame.

00:08.032 --> 00:10.401
But I applaud you, Megatron.

00:10.402 --> 00:14.038
You certainly made
a grand exit.

00:15.707 --> 00:18.876
Ah, soundwave.
Cue the audio/visual.

00:18.877 --> 00:21.546
I wish to address the troops.

00:24.516 --> 00:26.551
<i>The loss of Megatron,</i>

00:26.552 --> 00:30.488
<i>leader of the great
Decepticon uprising,</i>

00:30.489 --> 00:34.092
<i>is certainly a blow
to our cause.</i>

00:34.093 --> 00:39.030
<i>Yet we mustn't despair
over his tragic demise</i>

00:39.031 --> 00:44.402
<i>but instead embrace
his ultimate sacrifice</i>

00:44.403 --> 00:48.239
<i>and build upon the foundation
he laid</i>

00:48.240 --> 00:51.876
with an even mightier hand.

00:51.877 --> 00:53.644
With all due respect,

00:53.645 --> 00:57.381
<i>Commander Star--
Uh, lord Starscream.</i>

00:57.382 --> 00:59.650
Yes, yes. What is it?

00:59.651 --> 01:02.720
If we failed to conquer earth
under lord Megatron's command,

01:02.721 --> 01:03.988
what hope do we have now

01:03.989 --> 01:05.957
while the autobots
still defend it?

01:05.958 --> 01:09.994
Allow me to be crystal clear.

01:09.995 --> 01:14.532
I studied for millennia
under our former master.

01:14.533 --> 01:18.402
Thus, I am equipped
to lead you --

01:18.403 --> 01:21.973
I, Megatron's true heir,

01:21.974 --> 01:24.475
lord Starscream,

01:24.476 --> 01:27.712
emperor of destruction!

01:32.584 --> 01:35.319
What?

01:35.320 --> 01:38.389
What use are troops
who can't rise to the task

01:38.390 --> 01:42.593
of inflicting unspeakable
destruction in my name?

01:42.594 --> 01:44.795
Ah, but wait.

01:44.796 --> 01:48.766
Legend tells
of one capable warrior,

01:48.767 --> 01:53.371
one who exists here,
upon this very planet,

01:53.372 --> 01:58.242
one who can be student
to my master.

